				<td colspan="2"><span>With the difference than you are using a weapon, while still getting a 1.8 mod.
<br />

<br />
Now I'm not that high level yet, and I've desperately been trying to find a troubadour's mace for sale, but it certainly looks very nice...
<br />

<br />
For example, Warsong of Zek gives Attack Speed by 60%; Increase Strength by 36(L62) to 37(L65); Increase Attack by 17(L62) to 18(L65); Damage Shield by 15; according to this site.
<br />

<br />
Haste won't go up, but the str would go from 37 to 66.6, attack from 18 to 32.4 and damage shield from 15 to 23 (not assuming any other mods).  Those are some pretty nice boosts, and you can get all that while still using a weapon rather than having to swap out for instruments.  I think I'll be using the mace for a long time, since my personal damage isn't that great, but I can sure increase the damage my group is doing...</span></td>
